OriginalText.EditorialCommentary: Written larger in all voices (though in the same hand as the rest of the text)

Note.EditorialCommentary: At "cantores", ties have been written in VatS 42 to make a three-syllable phrase; the text in other versions is "vicarios" (and the previous phrase is "canonicos", which has been eliminated entirely in VatS 42).
